source.name: Hearing Office Average Processing Time Ranking Report
source.description: A ranking of ODAR hearing offices by the average number of days until final disposition of the hearing request. The average shown will be a combined average for all cases completed in that hearing office.  Users will be able determine where a particular hearing office stands among the total with respect to this workload category.
